### Sort by area descending
GET {{base}}/collections/cantons-postgis/items?f=json&sortby=-AREA_HA

### BBox: western Switzerland
GET {{base}}/collections/cantons-postgis/items?f=json&bbox=6.0,46.0,7.5,47.5

